Package com.flipfit.bean

Class User

java.lang.Object
com.flipfit.bean.User
public class User extends Object
The User class represents a user within the FlipFit system. This class is a **Plain Old Java Object (POJO)** that encapsulates user-related data, including personal details, contact information, and authentication credentials.

It provides two constructors: one for creating a new user (without a database-assigned ID) and another for instantiating a user object from an existing database record.
